{"tid":1900461,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"3月2號全面恢復駕駛考試(路試)筆試除外","createTime":"2020-02-27T08:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T18:47:44.000Z","uid":349167,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c5b1d9802ea6c99816649e52e35e42c838014956","tid":1900461,"uid":349167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T08:44:37.000Z","msg":"運輸署將於2/3/2020(星期一)全面恢復駕駛考試(路試)筆試除外，考生須於試前接受體温檢測，任何人於考試中心內及考試期間必須配戴口罩，進入辦公室前使用酒精搓手液清潔雙手，若考生沒有配戴口罩、拒絕接受體温檢測或體温檢測結果高於攝氏37.5度，有關考生將會被拒絕進入試場，其考試將會另行安排日期。另外，為使車箱內保持空氣流通，減少病毒傳播機會，考牌主任在考試期間可打開車窗。<br />\n                                  駕駛事務組<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟3月中都考路試啦 好緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b24929e90ad7dddcc571858be75006873c62892e","tid":1900461,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T08:53:13.000Z","msg":"林鄭都未話在家工作安排結束<br />\n老運算唔算偷步公佈"},{"pid":"77ce173216ba131cef882c2261c8cbcc1c468686","tid":1900461,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T08:54:01.000Z","msg":"你邊度見到?"},{"pid":"f9b1ca2058a89646dfe663799d74975b46d1fb74","tid":1900461,"uid":190954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T08:54:56.000Z","msg":"唔係今個月5號已經開翻咗咩？ 又停咗？<br />\n<br />\n利伸：6號考左"},{"pid":"6d8b7e1eec80b80fcbabff558ff5962f1e1a27fc","tid":1900461,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9b1ca2058a89646dfe663799d74975b46d1fb74","tid":1900461,"uid":190954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T08:54:56.000Z","msg":"唔係今個月5號已經開翻咗咩？ 又停咗？<br />\n<br />\n利伸：6號考左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T08:55:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/publications_and_press_releases/press_releases/transport_department/index_id_3358.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.td.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublications_and_press_releases%2Fpress_releases%2Ftransport_department%2Findex_id_3358.html&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKw